videos.description: Iowa's Jordan Bohannon with the great bounce pass to Tyler Cook for the jam on the break.
videos.headline: Iowa 's Bohannon with the great pass to Cook for the dunk

videos.description: Iowa keeps the ball alive after a missed 3-pointer and Nicholas Baer capitalizes with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Iowa's good hustle leads to a 3

videos.description: Wisconsin's Bronson Koenig air balls a deep 3 and teammate Brevin Pritzl retrieves the rebound and his shot ends up on the wrong side of the backboard.
videos.headline: Wisconsin has bad offensive sequence on the offensive end

videos.description: Iowa's Nicholas Baer hits 3-pointer in the final seconds of the first half to extend their lead as they head into the locker room.
videos.headline: Iowa's Baer hits 3-pointer in the final seconds of the first half

videos.description: Wisconsin's Nigel Hayes gets the ball down low and scores off glass while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Hayes drives for the and-1 bucket

videos.description: Wisconsin's Jordan Hill makes the steal and goes all the way for the dunk.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Hill gets the steal and slams it home

videos.description: Iowa's Ahmad Wagner steals the ball off the inbounds pass and lays it up with under a minute to go in the game.
videos.headline: Wagner steals the inbounds pass and scores

videos.description: Iowa gets the offensive rebound and Jordan Bohannon hits game-winning 3-pointer while Bronson Koenig cant hit the last second shot for Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Iowa's Bohannon hits go-ahead 3-pointer in final seconds

videos.description: Iowa's Jordan Bohannon talks about the team keeping their composure against No. 22 Wisconsin late in the game to upset the Badgers.
videos.headline: Bohannon talks about game-winning 3 against Wisconsin
